<worksheet><title>Geometric Series Applications</title>

<p>
	In this workshop we will:
</p>
<objectives>
	<ol>
		<li>
			<p>
				use the formula for the sum of a finite geometric series to solve a common real-life problem and 
			</p>
		</li>
		<li>
			<p>
				use the formula for the sum of an infinite geometric series to write a repeating decimal as a fraction.
			</p>
		</li>
